title: The Moon Awaits v1.0.8
description:
Explore the solar system in this explosive, fast paced action platformer!
Use your weapons, skill and whit to repair your ship and blast off into space!

Features -

. Explore the solar system!
. Randomly generated levels which change every play through
. Battle deadly space creatures
. Use a jetpack!
. Explosive weapons
. A robot companion!
. Take control of your ship and blast off into space
. Interact with the environment and shape levels
. Upgrade your character
. Compete in online leader boards
. An expanding universe
. Original soundtrack
. No annoying in-app purchases

What's New:

- Version 1.08 -
New ship features and better device scaling!
Have fun and report any issues. We will get them resolved as soon as possible!
- Dynamic zero

More info:
 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dynamiczero.themoonawaits
